00:40:22.560 --> 00:40:24.480
And then that's an 80-20 thing.

749
00:40:25.680 --> 00:40:27.000
What's an 80-20 thing?

750
00:40:29.000 --> 00:40:33.040
Where 80% of women
are attracted to 20% of men.

751
00:40:34.720 --> 00:40:37.720
[clears throat] But I do think
they're right about that. though.

752
00:40:41.720 --> 00:40:44.480
And lots of people
liked her comments quite a lot.

753
00:40:46.120 --> 00:40:48.600
Yeah. they thought it was funny.

754
00:40:50.040 --> 00:40:52.080
You must have found that quite cruel.

755
00:40:54.320 --> 00:40:55.520
I suppose.

756
00:40:55.600 --> 00:40:57.480
Did she do this to anyone else?

757
00:40:58.000 --> 00:41:00.200
- No.
- Well. why did she do it to you?

758
00:41:03.720 --> 00:41:05.840
Because… Because I'm ugly.

759
00:41:06.760 --> 00:41:10.720
- You think that's why she did it to you?
- Well. I'm the ugliest. I suppose. so…

760
00:41:12.320 --> 00:41:13.840
Did you ever call her on it?

761
00:41:14.360 --> 00:41:15.960
- Yeah.
- What did you say?

762
00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:21.240
I don't know.
"I'm not what you say I am." or…

763
00:41:21.320 --> 00:41:22.640
And what did she say?

764
00:41:23.920 --> 00:41:24.960
[sighs]

765
00:41:26.560 --> 00:41:27.520
She just…

766
00:41:28.360 --> 00:41:32.320
She just smiled and said. "Okay."
and walked away.

767
00:41:33.720 --> 00:41:35.480
And you never thought to tell anyone?

768
00:41:35.560 --> 00:41:38.160
- It's a bit late for that now.
- That just must have hurt.

769
00:41:38.240 --> 00:41:39.320
I didn't kill her.

770
00:41:40.600 --> 00:41:44.360
You think I did because you've seen
the video. You can't trust videos anymore.

771
00:41:44.440 --> 00:41:45.600
It's all fake news.

772
00:41:45.680 --> 00:41:47.760
- I'm not here to judge.
- I didn't kill her.

773
00:41:48.360 --> 00:41:50.560
She was a bitch. Even you can see that.

774
00:41:50.640 --> 00:41:52.680
I should've killed her.
but I didn't. I just…

775
00:41:53.200 --> 00:41:54.680
[clears throat]

776
00:41:54.760 --> 00:41:55.720
All… All I did…

777
00:41:56.240 --> 00:41:57.360
[sighs]

778
00:41:59.240 --> 00:42:00.480
All I did was…

779
00:42:02.240 --> 00:42:03.360
[sighs]

780
00:42:04.720 --> 00:42:05.840
[scoffs]

781
00:42:06.400 --> 00:42:07.600
Look at ya.

782
00:42:07.680 --> 00:42:10.280
All hopeful. like I'm gonna say
something important.

783
00:42:11.080 --> 00:42:13.080
[scoffs. sighs]

784
00:42:15.680 --> 00:42:16.560
All I did…

785
00:42:18.320 --> 00:42:21.000
I did ask her out… after the photo.

786
00:42:21.960 --> 00:42:24.360
I went round and said I was sorry
that they'd done that to her.

787
00:42:24.880 --> 00:42:27.080
Showing everyone her tits. Her chest.

788
00:42:27.760 --> 00:42:30.040
And I wanted to know
if she'd come to the fair with me.

789
00:42:31.480 --> 00:42:35.800
You know. I just thought
she might be weak. or that…

790
00:42:36.320 --> 00:42:38.240
I just thought she might be weak. so…

791
00:42:39.480 --> 00:42:40.480
[sighs]

792
00:42:40.560 --> 00:42:43.240
'Cause everyone was calling her slag.

793
00:42:43.320 --> 00:42:45.240
you know. or flat or whatever.

794
00:42:45.320 --> 00:42:47.760
so I thought
when she was. like. that. weak.

795
00:42:48.440 --> 00:42:50.840
she might… she might like me.

796
00:42:51.760 --> 00:42:52.840
[sighs]

797
00:42:53.440 --> 00:42:55.520
It's clever. don't you think?

798
00:42:55.600 --> 00:42:58.080
To ask her out
when everyone else didn't like her?

799
00:42:59.000 --> 00:43:01.360
Well. I went round
and said I was sorry and everything.

800
00:43:01.440 --> 00:43:03.120
That Fidget was a wanker.

801
00:43:03.720 --> 00:43:06.200
And I said I'd take her
to the fair if she liked.

802
00:43:06.960 --> 00:43:10.960
Her weakness made her more gettable.
was your theory?

803
00:43:12.840 --> 00:43:14.000
Mm-hmm. Yeah.

804
00:43:16.960 --> 00:43:18.960
I thought you said you didn't like her.

805
00:43:19.560 --> 00:43:23.840
Uh. she's flat. That's a fact.
But I didn't mind that. That's okay.

806
00:43:25.640 --> 00:43:27.880
I wore my best tracksuit
I could find. and…

807
00:43:28.800 --> 00:43:30.080
[sighs]

808
00:43:30.160 --> 00:43:33.040
I don't even know why I'm telling you
all this. but I just said.

809
00:43:33.120 --> 00:43:34.760
"You wanna come to the fair?"

810
00:43:34.840 --> 00:43:36.080
And what did she say?

811
00:43:38.800 --> 00:43:39.920
[sighs]

812
00:43:40.520 --> 00:43:41.520
She just…

813
00:43:43.160 --> 00:43:45.920
She just laughed
and said. "Oh. I'm not that desperate."

814
00:43:47.400 --> 00:43:49.720
And the emoji messages came after that?

815
00:43:51.760 --> 00:43:52.720
Uh. yeah.

816
00:43:53.240 --> 00:43:57.200
She was. let's say. attacking you
for presuming you could ask her out?

817
00:43:57.280 --> 00:43:59.440
- Your words.
- You think they're unfair?

818
00:44:00.000 --> 00:44:03.600
[hesitates] <i>You </i>think
she's a bitch. right?

819
00:44:04.120 --> 00:44:05.160
Doing all that.

820
00:44:05.840 --> 00:44:07.800
You think she's a bullying bitch.

821
00:44:08.520 --> 00:44:09.560
[sighs]

822
00:44:11.040 --> 00:44:13.520
She <i>was </i>a bullying bitch. right?

823
00:44:13.600 --> 00:44:16.000
But that's the thing. you see?

824
00:44:16.080 --> 00:44:18.200
That night. I didn't touch her.

825
00:44:19.960 --> 00:44:21.960
I could've touched her.
but I didn't. I just…

826
00:44:22.480 --> 00:44:25.560
I had a knife.
She was scared. But I didn't do that.

827
00:44:27.560 --> 00:44:31.720
I could have touched any part of her body.
I really wanted to. but I didn't. I just…

828
00:44:34.320 --> 00:44:36.000
Most boys would've touched her.

829
00:44:40.360 --> 00:44:41.720
So that makes me better.

830
00:44:46.240 --> 00:44:47.440
[softly] Don't you think?

831
00:45:03.160 --> 00:45:05.160
[rain pattering on roof]

832
00:45:21.480 --> 00:45:22.760
[sighs]

833
00:45:24.640 --> 00:45:26.960
I didn't… I didn't mean any of that.
I'm just tired.

834
00:45:27.040 --> 00:45:30.600
I'm talking too much.
I'm tired. I'm just… [sighs]

835
00:45:30.680 --> 00:45:33.040
I'm so. so tired.

836
00:45:35.520 --> 00:45:36.880
[sighs] I didn't kill her.

837
00:45:36.960 --> 00:45:39.280
Jamie. do you understand what death is?

838
00:45:40.120 --> 00:45:42.440
- What?
- Do you understand what death is?

839
00:45:43.520 --> 00:45:44.520
Yeah.

840
00:45:44.600 --> 00:45:47.080
You understand that Katie's gone
and she can't come back?

841
00:45:47.160 --> 00:45:48.280
I didn't do it.

842
00:45:48.800 --> 00:45:50.840
That whatever claims
you make as to her character--

843
00:45:50.920 --> 00:45:54.200
- I didn't mean she was a bitch.
- Whatever claims you make. she's gone.

844
00:45:55.280 --> 00:45:56.520
That whoever did kill her.

845
00:45:56.600 --> 00:45:59.240
they extinguished the possibility
of her future life.

846
00:46:03.040 --> 00:46:05.000
I didn't mean to be mean about her.
She just did--

847
00:46:05.080 --> 00:46:08.360
- Jamie. listen. Do you understand?
- She just didn't like me.

848
00:46:10.160 --> 00:46:12.040
Yeah. I'm not dumb.

849
00:46:13.560 --> 00:46:16.400
- Do you understand that murder is a crime?
- Yeah.

850
00:46:17.040 --> 00:46:20.320
You understand that if you're
found guilty. you'll be held in detention?

851
00:46:20.400 --> 00:46:23.240
- Who doesn't know that?
- Understand who will make the decision?

852
00:46:24.120 --> 00:46:26.360
- Judge. Jury.
- Okay.

853
00:46:33.720 --> 00:46:35.640
Jamie. this is our last session.

854
00:46:36.960 --> 00:46:37.800
What?

855
00:46:37.880 --> 00:46:39.840
- What I would encourage you to--
- No. Why?

856
00:46:39.920 --> 00:46:42.720
Take advantage of any mental health
services that are offered.

857
00:46:42.800 --> 00:46:44.680
- No. Why?
- I think you'll benefit.

858
00:46:44.760 --> 00:46:47.120
- No. I won't.
- Well. that's just what I think.

859
00:46:47.200 --> 00:46:49.640
And then you come back. You see me?

860
00:46:49.720 --> 00:46:51.840
Unfortunately. I'm needed elsewhere.

861
00:46:53.480 --> 00:46:57.440
- It's just fucking done. is it? All of it?
- I hope you take what I said seriously.

862
00:46:57.520 --> 00:47:00.600
- Thanks for your time. I'll ask Frank--
- Thanks for my time?

863
00:47:00.680 --> 00:47:04.280
- Frank! I'm grateful that you've spoken--
- You think I'm being honest?

864
00:47:04.360 --> 00:47:07.400
- Are you gonna tell the judge?
- I think you've spoken with honesty.

865
00:47:07.480 --> 00:47:09.600
But all I'm advising the judge on
is your understanding.

866
00:47:09.680 --> 00:47:12.760
My understanding. yes. [sighs]

867
00:47:14.600 --> 00:47:16.720
- It doesn't seem like a proper goodbye.
- [Briony] It is.

868
00:47:16.800 --> 00:47:18.880
- It doesn't seem like one.
- [Frank] That's enough.

869
00:47:18.960 --> 00:47:20.360
No. we haven't finished.

870
00:47:20.440 --> 00:47:22.640
- We have. Thank you. Frank.
- No. no! [sighs]

871
00:47:22.720 --> 00:47:24.160
Can I ask you something?

872
00:47:24.880 --> 00:47:25.800
Yes.

873
00:47:26.960 --> 00:47:27.960
[sighs]

874
00:47:28.760 --> 00:47:31.160
[hesitates] Do you like me?

875
00:47:42.080 --> 00:47:45.280
- I was here as a professional. Jamie.
- Don't you think like that. then?

876
00:47:45.360 --> 00:47:48.320
- My job was to assess you.
- Because I like you.

877
00:47:48.400 --> 00:47:50.840
Not like that.
Not fancying you. Just as a person.

878
00:47:50.920 --> 00:47:53.680
- [guard] Okay. son. come on.
- No. don't you even like me a bit?

879
00:47:53.760 --> 00:47:55.560
What did you think about me. then?

880
00:47:56.160 --> 00:47:58.680
- Decide. come on!
- [Briony] This was really useful.

881
00:47:58.760 --> 00:48:00.960
Don't you go fucking telling them
I did it!

882
00:48:01.040 --> 00:48:02.520
- Don't you dare!
- Whoa. come on.

883
00:48:02.600 --> 00:48:05.800
Don't you go fucking…
Get the fuck off me! Don't you dare!

884
00:48:05.880 --> 00:48:07.120
- Hey!
- Fuck!

885
00:48:07.200 --> 00:48:09.840
- Come on. Jamie. man. please.
- Don't you even like me a bit?

886
00:48:09.920 --> 00:48:11.000
Okay? Jamie. come on.

887
00:48:11.080 --> 00:48:13.080
- What did you think about me. then?
- Okay.

888
00:48:13.160 --> 00:48:14.800
Just tell my dad I'm all right!

889
00:48:15.480 --> 00:48:18.200
- Tell him that I'm okay!
- [guard] Jamie. you're hurting yourself.

890
00:48:18.280 --> 00:48:20.520
- [Jamie] Tell him that I'm all right!
- [guard] Calm down.

891
00:48:20.600 --> 00:48:21.840
[Jamie] Tell him I'm all right!

892
00:48:21.920 --> 00:48:24.680
- Tell him I'm okay. please!
- [guard shouting]

893
00:48:24.760 --> 00:48:27.440
[whimpers. exhales shakily]

894
00:48:36.200 --> 00:48:37.640
[sighs deeply]

895
00:48:43.440 --> 00:48:46.480
[takes a slow. deep breath]

896
00:48:49.400 --> 00:48:51.400
[crying softly]

897
00:48:57.480 --> 00:48:59.480
[breath grows steady]

898
00:49:28.920 --> 00:49:30.040
[sniffles]

899
00:49:36.240 --> 00:49:37.880
[groans]

900
00:49:37.960 --> 00:49:39.400
Oh God.

901
00:49:40.760 --> 00:49:41.920
[huffs]

902
00:49:47.160 --> 00:49:49.240
[sighs. sniffles]

903
00:49:54.880 --> 00:49:57.000
[somber instrumental music playing]

904
00:50:04.720 --> 00:50:06.720
[rain pattering loudly]

905
00:50:15.680 --> 00:50:19.560
[somber music continues]
